2.THEN WE APPLY JQUERY TO ALL THE TOGGLE BUTTONS
( $(.toggleButton).hover(function()) { 
  $(this).css("background-color", "grey");
}
- this is simple function to hover 
- we can always check jquery documentation at api.jquery.com

3.THEN WE CREATE TEXTAREA IN HTML AND WE SORT OUT STYLE IN CSS
4.THEN WE CAN GOOGLE STACKOVERFLOW AND FIND HOW TO CHANGE CONTENT INSIDE CONTAINERS TEXTAREA
( just an example : $("frameid").contents().find("html").html("my html");)
5.THEN UPDATE CONTENT FROM TEXTAREA AND UPDATE VALUE IMMIDIATLY AFTER
WE TYPE THE CODE
6.MAKE CSS JAVASCRIPT AND OUTPUT TO HAPPEN 
7.WE USE JAVASCRIPT EVAL() FUNCTION TO RUN JAVASCRIPT WHICH EVALUTES STRING OF JS
8.WE ADD IT TO OUR UPDATE OUTPUT
9.IT WILL EVALUTE CODE 
